{"tid":2138393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有中學校長稱網教要顧及專注力 憂學生欠群體生活","createTime":"2020-08-03T14:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T14:15:45.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a48f8c16112c01ab82cf1544b855f2f969a4d66e","tid":2138393,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"有中學校長稱網教要顧及專注力 憂學生欠群體生活<br />\n2020-08-03 HKT 21:23<br />\n<br />\n&quot;教育局宣布，因應疫情，學校需於新學年暫停校內面授課程及活動，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n柴灣的中華傳道會劉永生中學校長林達豪關注，早前停課至今，在沒有群體及校園生活下，擔心學生心理素質會受影響......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;林達豪提到，展開網上教學時，需要保護學生的眼睛健康，亦要考慮學生是否有足夠專注力，因此將縮短課堂時間；同時亦會支援有特別學習需要或經濟需要的學生。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541621-20200803.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541621-20200803.htm&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=1bc7dca6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541621-20200803.htm&h=e9a57588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541621-20200803.htm</a>"}]}